text: Igor Kashurov (Russian: Игорь Кашуров; born 3 April 1951) is a Soviet rower. He competed at the 1972 Summer Olympics in Munich with the men's coxless four where they came fourth. ==References== Category:1951 births Category:Living people Category:Soviet male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of the Soviet Union Category:Rowers at the 1972 Summer Olympics
